In a message dated 2/24/03 10:54:33 PM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> Hydras continue kissing her, but now he huged thighly. The craw slipped and 
> didn't damaged his armor.
> 

Clinging to him now, as she returned the kiss with equal passion. 

How did it come to this? In a way she wanted to know, in another she didn't 
care. Either way, she could feel the burning her in lasercore, her spark of a 
unity. Ever since she first laid her optics upon Megatron... it had been such 
a desire in her. But... again, as a Decepticon, her sacrifice to be the best 
warrior came first. 

Then.. all things disappeared from her mind, her meta processor. Only to 
cling to him, hold him, barely feeling their exocovers against eachother as a 
tingling sensation rushed through her. 

Purring into the deep, passionate kiss. Allowing for the first time to let 
such things to take her away, to distract her.. to overwhelm her.
